1.subject: Kamala Devi Harris
facts: is an American politician and attorney.
serves as the 49th vice president of the United States since 2021, alongside President Joe Biden.
is the first female vice president in U.S. history.
is also the highest-ranking female official in U.S. history.
is both the first African American and the first Asian American vice president.
served as a U.S. senator from California between 2017 and 2021.
was the attorney general of California.
is the Democratic Party's presidential nominee in the 2024 U.S. presidential election.
